OL,3,CCross-examination of alleged victim
OL,4,Ccontinues in Jeffrey Donaldson trial
OL,6,FA woman has told the Sir Jeffrey
OL,7,FDonaldson trial that the former DUP
OL,8,Fleader touched her breasts while she
OL,9,Fwas a child.
OL,11,FChallenged by a barrister over
OL,12,F"inconsistencies" between her evidence
OL,13,Fin court and what she had told a
OL,14,Fpolice officer, Complainant A insisted
OL,15,F"the facts are the facts".
OL,17,FDonaldson, 63, is on trial at Newry
OL,18,FCrown Court accused of rape and
OL,19,Fseveral counts of gross indecency and
OL,20,Fof indecent assault.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@QO]wD@AOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
