OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780085153
OL,3,CCross-examination of alleged victim
OL,4,Ccontinues in Jeffrey Donaldson trial
OL,6,FThe ex-MP has pleaded not guilty to
OL,7,Fthe 18 alleged offences.
OL,9,FThe charges span a time period between
OL,10,F1985 and 2008 involving two alleged
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,FDonaldson's wife, Lady Eleanor
OL,14,FDonaldson denies several charges of
OL,15,Faiding and abetting her husband's
OL,16,Falleged offending.
OL,18,FShe is facing a trial of the facts
OL,19,Fafter Judge Paul Ramsey ruled her
OL,20,Funfit to stand trial on mental health
OL,21,Fgrounds.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780085153
OL,3,CCross-examination of alleged victim
OL,4,Ccontinues in Jeffrey Donaldson trial
OL,6,FThe trial of the facts will test the
OL,7,Fevidence in the case, but cannot
OL,8,Fresult in a criminal conviction.
OL,10,FKieran Vaughan KC, barrister for
OL,11,FJeffrey Donaldson, continued his cross-
OL,12,Fexamination of Complainant A, one of
OL,13,Fthe two alleged victims, on Friday.
OL,15,FDonaldson sat in the dock wearing a
OL,16,Fdark grey suit and yellow tie,
OL,17,Foccasionally taking notes.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
