CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780085153
OL,3,CCross-examination of alleged victim
OL,4,Ccontinues in Jeffrey Donaldson trial
OL,6,FMr Vaughan referred to an allegation
OL,7,Fmade by the woman that Donaldson had
OL,8,Ftouched her breasts on a number of
OL,9,Foccasions when she was of primary
OL,10,Fschool age.
OL,12,FHe asked about her claim that she had
OL,13,Fbeen touched.
OL,15,FShe said: "Mostly, one or two
OL,16,Foccasions when it was over the top of
OL,17,Fa bra."
OL,26,@wD@KOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780085153
OL,3,CCross-examination of alleged victim
OL,4,Ccontinues in Jeffrey Donaldson trial
OL,6,FThe barrister drew attention to a
OL,7,Fmeeting Complainant A had had with a
OL,8,Fpolice officer where she mentioned
OL,9,F"touching over clothing".
OL,11,FShe said: "If that is what she has
OL,12,Fwritten, that is what was said."
OL,14,FMr Vaughan said: "On the face of it
OL,15,Fthat is inconsistent with what you
OL,16,Ftold the jury yesterday, about
OL,17,Ftouching under clothes."
OL,19,FShe said: "The facts are the facts, I
OL,20,Fam sticking to that."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@XO]sD@KOUtD@`O]vD@ROUyD@XO]{D@
OL,26,AKOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
