OL,3,CCross-examination of alleged victim
OL,4,Ccontinues in Jeffrey Donaldson trial
OL,6,FThe trial, which is expected to last
OL,7,Fbetween three and four weeks,
OL,8,Fcontinues.
OL,10,FJeffrey Donaldson, a former long-
OL,11,Fstanding MP for Lagan Valley, was
OL,12,Farrested and charged at the end of
OL,13,FMarch 2024.
OL,15,FHe resigned as DUP leader and was
OL,16,Fsuspended from the party after the
OL,17,Fallegations emerged.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
